name: Mad Catz The Authentic E.S. Pro+ - Headset - in-ear - over-the-ear mount - wired - 3.5 mm jack | Dell USA
description: Mad Catz' E.S. PRO+ Gaming Earbuds pack the performance of full-size headsets for PC into a small form factor. Unlike most PC headsets in both function and design, E.S. PRO+ is a versatile gamer connecting to console controllers as well as smart devices. A larger-than-most 13.5mm driver delivers tournament-grade sound quality. And, two microphones give you total control of all your online conversations. E.S. PRO+ gaming headphones with mic are comfortable and provide the means to communicate with online friends and rivals alike. You get an assortment of different earbud sizes that let you discover the ideal fit. Plus, inner ear supports ensure the buds stay just where you want them so you can focus on the game.WARNING: Cancer - www.P65Warnings.ca.gov
